<h2 id="100">1. About Mediamarkt</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The Mediamarkt Plugin connects the marketplace Mediamarkt with your plentymarkets system. This enables you to automatically exchange item and order data between plentymarkets and Mediamarkt. This way, you can list your items on Mediamarkt.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="200">2. Registering with Mediamarkt</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You need your Mediamarkt access data consisting of the user name and password. You will receive this data from Mediamarkt. First, you need to become a <a href="https://www.mediamarkt.de/de/about-us/marketplace" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mediamarkt</a> and create a Mediamarkt account.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
