<h3 id="1220">6.2. Creating the leadtime to ship property</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>For each variation, you need to export a leadtime to ship in days to Mediamarkt. This way, you can tell Mediamarkt how many days you need to ship a variation. Mediamarkt accepts values between 1 and 45.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
